Description: An R client to MET Norway's 'Frost' API <https://frost.met.no/index.html> 
    The 'Frost' API, and the underlying data, is  made available by the Norwegian 
    Meteorological Institute (MET Norway). The data and products are distributed 
    under the Norwegian License for Open Data 2.0 (NLOD) <https://data.norge.no/nlod/en/2.0>
    and Creative Commons 4.0 <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/>.
